702694f-a.title: Brooklyn: 29th Street (East) - Albemarle Road
702694f-a.text:
2901-2903 East 29th Strect, at and adjoining the S.E. corner of
Albemarle Road. The view also shows Albemarle Road, at and adjoining
the S.E. corner of East 29th Street. Houses concerned are frame.
March 29, 1932.
P. L. Sperr.
NO REPRODUCTIONS.
